name: GNSS Data Repository
description: GNSS data collected by Continuously Operating Reference Station (CORS) is made available in RINEX files and in real-time NTRIP streams. Data includes daily, hourly, high-rate observation and navigation files, with sample rates from 1 to 30 seconds. Access methods include SFTP, S3, Web API, and web applications. All data is public under Creative Commons Attribution 3.0 Australia Licence.
